{"tid":369852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英政壇人明絕食　發起撐雙學三子請願| 本土新聞","createTime":"2017-08-22T15:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T16:33:04.000Z","uid":35842,"like":348,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb2bc1e4d600209314ca95e49aaf7238757b497","tid":369852,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"就爭取真普選而引發雨傘革命的雙學三子抗爭判囚案，英國保守黨人權委員會副主席班尼迪克&bull;羅哲斯（Benedict Rogers）號召英國民眾於明天（英國時間周三，二十三日下午一時）到英國外交部辦事處門外請願，抗議「香港法治和基本自由被毀及英國政府沉默處理」，要求外相鮑里斯&bull;約翰遜（Boris Johnson）為入獄三子說話，向中國施壓，促其尊重一國兩制。羅哲斯本人更會為港以斷食祈禱方式絕食。（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/08/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E6%94%BF%E7%95%8C%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%92%90%E9%9B%99%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90%E3%80%80%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F08%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2592%2590%25E9%259B%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AD%2590%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%25AD%2F&d=a7q6WjsThaM3dk12%2FWXHyzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=fef82b26\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/08/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E6%94%BF%E7%95%8C%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%92%90%E9%9B%99%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90%E3%80%80%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%AD/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684040251a6c98ba7e3270ad141505715a3d0769","tid":369852,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667723c54afe92bdfaf5e1161705d1